<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/jul/03/">&#x27a0;</a> July 3, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="sox-win-extra-bases" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/extras/extra_bases/2007/07/sox_win.html">Sox win - Extra Bases</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;The Sox ended their first half at 50-31, which was also their record last year.&#8221; And we all remember how last year turned out.  This is why Red Sox Nation is only cautiously optimistic about our 10.5-game lead on the AL East.</p>

