<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/apr/25/">&#x27a0;</a> April 25, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="cabs-logan-travelers-go-green" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.thebostonchannel.com/money/12931665/detail.html?rss=bos&amp;psp=news">Cabs, Logan Travelers Go Green - WCVB Boston</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Interesting attempt by the City of Boston to encourage hybrid taxis &#8212; They&#8217;ll get to cut to the front of the taxi queue at Logan Airport.  Hybrid car owners get &#8220;preferred parking&#8221; too.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
